name: mega_loop_while_array_index_sum
section: codegen-control-loops
args: 
type: Bool
expect: True
description: while induction variable must index env array and mutate accumulator.
law: (= (with [xs [2 4 6] i 0 sum 0] (do (while (< i 3) (begin (set! sum (+ sum (xs i))) (set! i (+ i 1)))) sum)) 12)
